data.title: EUROPEAN HISTORY 1870TO 1945 Pamphlet
data.meta_description: EUROPEAN_HISTORY_1870TO_1945_pamphlet - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides information about European history from 1870 to 1945. It discusses the unification of Germany under Bismarck through a series of wars from 1864 to 1871. It also examines Bismarck's domestic policies which aimed to consolidate power and eliminate opposition through laws targeting Catholics and Socialists. Bismarck enacted social reforms to benefit workers and introduced policies of Germanization. In foreign policy, Bismarck created alliances to isolate France and maintain peace in Europe through German strength.
